{"tid":1511111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《舒特拉的名單》女演員  : 被香港的年輕示威者深深打動","createTime":"2019-08-27T12:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:45.000Z","uid":134071,"like":594,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"1176c0fcec30b75ff439c99751de65e783352701","tid":1511111,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/jozev1969/posts/10156585723576009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjozev1969%2Fposts%2F10156585723576009&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=7248d194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/jozev1969/posts/10156585723576009</a><br />\n<br />\n喬靖夫<br />\n8小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【手動share】<br />\n<br />\n//曾經參演《舒特拉的名單》的波蘭女演員 Anna Mucha 早前來過香港，並親身見證過反送中示威。事後她接受訪問時，表示自己被香港的年輕示威者深深打動。<br />\n<br />\nMucha 特別提及佔領機場一役，儘管有旅客埋怨航班受阻帶來不便，不過當時同樣滯留機場的 Mucha 就表示諒解，甚至幫忙向媒體解釋，香港人正在為自己的生命奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n報道原文為波蘭文。有舊同事希望多點香港人看到 Mucha 的支持，很有心將整篇報道譯成英文，期望有本地傳媒報道。我也略盡綿力在此引介一下，希望有同行用得著罷。<br />\n<br />\n也請大家幫忙廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n英文譯文：<br />\n<br />\nPolish celebrity about protesting Hongkongers: They are fighting for their lives&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAnna Mucha, Polish actress known to Western audiences as the character Danka Dresner (the little girl with the round glasses) in the film &ldquo;Schindler&rsquo;s List&rdquo; directed by Steven Spielberg, in a conversation with a Polish media outlet Polsat News mentioned her recent visit to Hong Kong and talked about protests there.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Despite the fact that there were 2 million people on the street demonstrating their dissatisfaction with and their expectation from Mainland China and the government, I was under an impression that everything was going on in a moderate way.&rdquo;, Mucha stated.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to the Polish celebrity, the protesters are well-organized. &ldquo;When I entered Hong Kong, I received a schedule stating at what time and at what places we can expect protests. The protesters are mainly young people under age of 25. They have a huge support of their society. The situation does not look good but those protesting young people really moved me.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nAnna Mucha said that from the travellers&rsquo; perspective, protests in Hong Kong maybe a nuisance because they might disrupt flights in and out of Hong Kong but as Anna, who herself was stuck in the airport explained &ldquo;Hongkongers are fighting for their lives&rdquo;..//"},{"pid":"e51ac32fa7b4745f25a44f25e3a2fedd7cda4129","tid":1511111,"uid":134071,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"《舒特拉的名單》好經典.  睇一次喊一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iarykvuRCkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiarykvuRCkc&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=9296b77b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iarykvuRCkc</a>"},{"pid":"b4a69047bb376cdf804da25b9bb695f9db7c1d14","tid":1511111,"uid":263161,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"058d32576bf34ec8fe9bd4dc09cb9cb4cff004b3","tid":1511111,"uid":263161,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cba0ccb5b20fa7c9b551a785eb1e8ed756e5de44","tid":1511111,"uid":287449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"經濟抗爭！揸現金，換美金，轉mpf，唔消費，每逢星期五同星期日都係全民宵禁日，不出街不消費！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭有張良計，我地有過牆梯－全民參與行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510140</a><br />\n<br />\n真正中共、港共春袋！金融/經濟抗爭1-page 懶人包登場！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dKNMmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dKN